text_raw:
2. The 19th day of May 2025 is appointed as the day on which paragraphs 
(a), (b), (c), (d) and (e) of section 21 of the Road Traffic Act 2024 (No. 10 of 
2024) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 May, 2025. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 
Minister for Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 16th May, 2025.
